00:06:47.700 --> 00:06:48.910
We were Mormons.

00:06:48.910 --> 00:06:51.540
And growing up in Michigan, that
might have seemed unusual

00:06:51.540 --> 00:06:52.400
or out of place.

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:55.020
But I really don't remember
it that way.

00:06:55.020 --> 00:06:57.660
My friends cared more about what
